data.description: Discover your dream home in the heart of Moss Bluff. This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a versatile office and bonus room, providing ample space for your family's needs. This home seamlessly blends comfort and functionality.  Step into the heart of this home, and you'll find a living room that exudes warmth and comfort. Large windows allow natural light to cascade into the room, highlighting the well-appointed details.  A focal point of the living room is a charming fireplace, providing both visual appeal and a cozy ambiance. Whether you're unwinding after a long day or hosting friends and family, this living room offers the perfect setting. The neutral color palette and thoughtfully chosen finishes create a versatile backdrop, allowing you to personalize the space to suit your style.  The bedrooms in this home are designed with your comfort in mind. The primary bedroom is a spacious retreat, featuring ample natural light and a thoughtfully planned layout that allows for various furniture arrangements. A private en-suite bathroom offers convenience and a touch of luxury.  The two additional bedrooms are generously sized, providing plenty of space for family members or guests. With well-appointed closets, there's no shortage of storage for your wardrobe and personal belongings.  But the allure doesn't stop there—imagine endless summer fun with the above-ground children's pool, creating memories that will last a lifetime. The fenced-in backyard ensures privacy and security, perfect for gatherings or peaceful relaxation. Don't miss the opportunity to call this house your home and experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and educational excellence in the renowned Sam Houston school district. AGENT SEE REMARKS
